name: Butyryl-coA reductase (NADH)
rxn_str: btcoa_c + h_c + nadh_c <=> btal_c + coa_c + nad_c

name: Pyruvate dehydrogenase
rxn_str: coa_c + nad_c + pyr_c <=> accoa_c + co2_c + nadh_c

name: Acetaldehyde dehydrogenase (acetylating)
rxn_str: acald_c + coa_c + nad_c <=> accoa_c + h_c + nadh_c

name: Methylmalonate-semialdehyde dehydrogenase (malonic semialdehyde)
rxn_str: coa_c + msa_c + nad_c <=> accoa_c + co2_c + nadh_c

name: Methylmalonate-semialdehyde dehydrogenase (propanol)
rxn_str: coa_c + nad_c + ppal_c <=> h_c + nadh_c + ppcoa_c
